{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017cRoXcWk3HUUuTUSG418CM","type":"tool_result","content":"Usage\n\nrabbitmqctl [--node <node>] [--longnames] [--quiet] set_policy [--vhost <vhost>] [--priority <priority>] [--apply-to <apply-to>] <name> <pattern> <definition>\n\nSets or updates a policy.\n\n\nArguments and Options\n\n<name>\n\tpolicy name (identifier)\n\n<pattern>\n\tregular expression pattern that will be used to match queues, exchanges, etc\n\n<definition>\n\tpolicy definition (arguments). Must be a valid JSON document\n\n--priority <priority>\n\tpolicy priority\n\n--apply-to <queues | exchanges | all>\n\tpolicy should only apply to queues, exchanges, or all entities (both of the above)\n\n\nRelevant Doc Guides\n\n * https://rabbitmq.com/docs/parameters/\n\n\nGeneral Options\n\nThe following options are accepted by most or all commands.\n\nshort            | long          | description\n-----------------|---------------|--------------------------------\n-?               | --help        | displays command help\n-n <node>        | --node <node> | connect to node <node>\n-l               | --longnames   | use long host names","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e959a181-dc9c-42cf-a219-332ca244b82f","uuid":"eb217869-1fe6-4a56-9ef5-21d3f9dc58b6","timestamp":"2026-07-02T10:05:35.818Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"Usage\n\nrabbitmqctl [--node <node>] [--longnames] [--quiet] set_policy [--vhost <vhost>] [--priority <priority>] [--apply-to <apply-to>] <name> <pattern> <definition>\n\nSets or updates a policy.\n\n\nArguments and Options\n\n<name>\n\tpolicy name (identifier)\n\n<pattern>\n\tregular expression pattern that will be used to match queues, exchanges, etc\n\n<definition>\n\tpolicy definition (arguments). Must be a valid JSON document\n\n--priority <priority>\n\tpolicy priority\n\n--apply-to <queues | exchanges | all>\n\tpolicy should only apply to queues, exchanges, or all entities (both of the above)\n\n\nRelevant Doc Guides\n\n * https://rabbitmq.com/docs/parameters/\n\n\nGeneral Options\n\nThe following options are accepted by most or all commands.\n\nshort            | long          | description\n-----------------|---------------|--------------------------------\n-?               | --help        | displays command help\n-n <node>        | --node <node> | connect to node <node>\n-l               | --longnames   | use long host names","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
